frameDefinitions: A Communicator or Medium assigns linguistic meaning to an Unresolved_referent thereby identifying the specific actor or entity which fulfills the answer to this question.
A Part is considered to be a member of the set described by the Total.
An Entity that is previously not visible to a Perceiver becomes visible.
An Item comes to be attached to a Goal, with a Connector forming a bond between the Handle of the Item and the Goal (or some part of it).

An Item is located at the top end of a scale of importance or social rank (or some other Attribute) in comparison to other members of a Contrast_set (usually, implicit) that is otherwise similar in kind to the Item.
A Location is filled or covered with the Theme.
frameExamples: Can you <t>name</t> all the U.S. Presidents?
Dr. Nelson <t>numbers</t> among the world?s foremost geotechnical engineering experts.
The armada <t>appeared</t> on the horizon at sunset.
According to plan, the front part of the hull quietly <t>attached</t> to the docking gear.
The <t>main</t> problem is that the administration has not yet clarified 'Regime change.' INI
The waters of the bay <t>teemed</t> with fish.
listRoleDefinitions: The person who uses language in the written or spoken modality to convey the <fen>Unresolved_referent</fen> to another person.
The thing to which the <fen>Communicator</fen> or <fen>Medium</fen> refers for identification purposes.
The physical or abstract setting in which the <fen>Unresolved_referent</fen> is conveyed.
When the the <fen>Communicator</fen> is makes the indication.
The location where the <fen>Communicator</fen> or <fen>Medium</fen> indicates the <fen>Unresolved_referent</fen>.
The complex multi-part entity of which a constituent <fen>Part</fen> is specified.
A subset of the <fen>Total</fen>.
The <fen>Time</fen> at which the subset relation holds.
The <fen>Place</fen> at which the subset relation holds.
The thing that the <fen>Perceiver</fen> is able to see or recognize.
A temporal description of the event of the <fen>Entity</fen> becoming visible.
The physical location in which the <fen>Entity</fen> becomes visible.
<fen>Connector</fen> identifies the  instrument used to attach, usually in a <ment>with</ment>-PP.
<fen>Item</fen> identifies the entity that comes to be attached to the <fen>Goal</fen>.
<fen>Items</fen> identifies the plural items that are tied together, resulting in their mutual attachment.
<fen>Goal</fen> identifies the location to which the first <fen>Item</fen> is attached.
The time when the attaching event takes place.
The location where the attaching event takes place.
An <fen>Item</fen> is the foremost thing in the <fen>Contrast_set</fen>.
This role identifies the domain (usually temporally or spatially defined) within which the <fen>Item</fen> is primary among its kind.
The <fen>Contrast_set</fen> is a group of entities similar to the <fen>Item</fen> out of which the <fen>Item</fen> is the most preeminent.
The <fen>Theme</fen> covers or fills the <fen>Location</fen>.  This role most frequently occurs in a PP Complement headed by with or in.
<fen>Location</fen> is the object or area that the <fen>Theme</fen> fills or covers.  This frame element generally occurs as the External Argument.
The period of time during which the the Abounding_with event occurs.
listRoleExamples: <fex>When this is resolved</fex>, I will name the winner.
As a representative in Congress in the years 1783-85, Gerry numbered <fex>among those who had possessed talent as Revolutionary agitators and wartime leaders</fex>.
Just be glad that <fex>you</fex> number among the living.
<fex>At that time</fex>, the factory numbered among the largest in the western half of North America.
<fex>In Europe</fex>, the sport counts among the economic branches of industry which generate employment among the young people.
The remoras attach to the whale <fex>with their strong jaws</fex>.
The remoras attach <fex>to the underside of the whale</fex>.
The foremost band <fex>in the world of the 1960's</fex> was clearly the Beatles.
Our discussion has raised a number of issues, foremost <fex>among them</fex> time.
The waters of the bay teemed <fex>with fish</fex>.
<fex>The walls</fex> crawled with nanite surveillance probes.
